Greens deputy Adam Bandt defends bushfire attack on Tony Abbott.
Aboriginals have used fires for fuel reduction for thousands of years, why are the Greens so against our history and culture?
They're not against fuel reduction, firing of the bush has been in practice for thousands of years and the current ecosystem has come to rely on it.
